{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/snapptheming.SnappTheming\/documentation\/SnappTheming"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SnappThemingColorDeclarations","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" = "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SnappThemingDeclarations","identifier":"doc:\/\/snapptheming.SnappTheming\/documentation\/SnappTheming\/SnappThemingDeclarations","preciseIdentifier":"s:12SnappTheming0aB12DeclarationsV"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/snapptheming.SnappTheming\/documentation\/SnappTheming\/SnappThemingColorRepresentation","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SnappThemingColorRepresentation","preciseIdentifier":"s:12SnappTheming0aB19ColorRepresentationO"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"SnappThemingColorConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/snapptheming.SnappTheming\/documentation\/SnappTheming\/SnappThemingColorConfiguration","preciseIdentifier":"s:12SnappTheming0aB18ColorConfigurationV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Colors can be declared as child properties of the root-level "},{"code":"colors","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property, as follows:"}]},{"syntax":"json","type":"codeListing","code":["{","    \"colors\": {","        \"appPrimary\": \"#FF0000\"","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The framework supports HEX-ecoded RGB, RGBA and ARGB notations. All of the following are valid entries:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["{","    \"colors\": {","        \"appPrimary\": \"#FF0000\",","        \"appSecondary\": \"#FF00000A\",","        \"appTertiary\": \"#0AFF0000\",","        \"appQuaternary\": \"#0F0\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Certain themes may require support for the system dark mode. In such cases, you can utilize the following annotation (again, HEX, RGBA, and ARGB colors are all supported here):"}]},{"code":["{","    \"colors\": {","        \"appPrimary\": {","            \"light\": \"#FF0000\", ","            \"dark\": \"#CC0000\"","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"json","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The mixing of color declaration styles is also supported. The following is a valid construct:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["{","    \"colors\": {","        \"appPrimary\": {","            \"light\": \"#FF0000\", ","            \"dark\": \"#CC0000\"","        },","        \"appSecondary\": \"#FF00000A\",","    }","}"],"syntax":"json"},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In the example above the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"appSecondary"},{"text":" color will be initialized with a value of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#FF00000A"},{"text":" which will be used in both the system light and dark modes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Providing hints on the color format to the parser","type":"heading","anchor":"Providing-hints-on-the-color-format-to-the-parser"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In general, decoding colors correctly should be automatic. The parser can handle various HEX-driven color declarations. Both ","type":"text"},{"code":"#FFF","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"#FFFFFF","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" annotations will be recognized and supported by default. The parser also defaults to recognizing RGBA color annotations (e.g., "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#FFFFFF0A"},{"text":"). If you need to support ARGB, please provide the correct value to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/snapptheming.SnappTheming\/documentation\/SnappTheming\/SnappThemingParserConfiguration\/colorFormat"},{"text":" property of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/snapptheming.SnappTheming\/documentation\/SnappTheming\/SnappThemingParserConfiguration"},{"type":"text","text":" (see "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/snapptheming.SnappTheming\/documentation\/SnappTheming\/SnappThemingColorFormat","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for the list of supported values)."}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/snapptheming.SnappTheming\/documentation\/SnappTheming\/SnappThemingColorDeclarations","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Responsible for managing and resolving color tokens, including static colors and dynamic system colors, with support for light\/dark mode."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/snapptheming\/snappthemingcolordeclarations"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:12SnappTheming0aB17ColorDeclarationsa","modules":[{"name":"SnappTheming"}],"symbolKind":"typealias","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SnappThemingColorDeclarations","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SnappThemingColorDeclarations"}],"title":"SnappThemingColorDeclarations","roleHeading":"Type Alias"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://snapptheming.SnappTheming/documentation/SnappTheming/SnappThemingColorDeclarations":{"url":"\/documentation\/snapptheming\/snappthemingcolordeclarations","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SnappThemingColorDeclarations"}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"SnappThemingColorDeclarations","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"SnappThemingColorDeclarations","identifier":"doc:\/\/snappthemi